{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_001", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "大明洪武年间，一个小村庄里，少年张陵正在院子里练武。他每天天不亮就起来扎马步。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "村头的老铁匠路过，看了半天说：'你这样练十年也成不了高手。'张陵不服气。老铁匠拿起一根烧火棍，随手一挥就在石墩上留下了深深的印记。张陵看呆了。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "练武-被指点-展示实力，隐士高人在民间", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_002", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "县令大人下乡体察民情，村民们都跪迎。只有李老汉还在田里锄地。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "随从要呵斥李老汉，县令摆摆手，走过去问：'老人家为何不跪？'李老汉头也不抬：'膝盖硬，弯不下去。'县令不但没生气，反而觉得这老农不一般。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "县令下乡-农人不跪-不卑不亢-引起注意", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_003", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "三国时期，刘备三顾茅庐请诸葛亮出山。前两次都没见到人。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "第三次刘备终于见到了诸葛亮。两人在草庐中谈了一夜，诸葛亮分析了天下大势，提出了三分天下的策略。刘备听完后激动地握住诸葛亮的手说：'我得先生如鱼得水！'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "三顾茅庐-隆中对-得人才，经典历史场景", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_004", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "大唐贞观年间，长安城里的东西两市热闹非凡。胡商们在叫卖着香料和宝石。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个吐蕃商人带来了几匹汗血宝马，引得众人围观。李白也在人群中，他当场即兴赋诗一首，赞美天马的雄姿。胡商虽然听不太懂，但连连鼓掌。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "长安街市-胡商-李白赋诗，盛唐气象", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_005", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "大宋年间，苏轼被贬到黄州。他在东坡上开了一块地种田。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "苏轼每天扛着锄头下地，与农民谈天说地。他在诗中写道：'莫听穿林打叶声，何妨吟啸且徐行。'虽然被贬，但他活得比谁都豁达。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "被贬-种田-豁达-写诗，文人风骨", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_006", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "汉武帝要远征匈奴，朝中大臣纷纷反对，说劳民伤财。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "卫青站出来说：'匈奴屡犯我边境，杀害我百姓，此仇不可不报。'武帝拍案而起：'卫青说得对！朕意已决。'他任命卫青为大将军，率军出征。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "朝堂争论-主战-决定-出征，历史决策", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_007", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "朱元璋年轻时在皇觉寺当和尚。一天他扫地时扫出了一块石板。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "石板上刻着几行字，他看不懂。老住持看了看，脸色一变，把石板藏了起来。多年后朱元璋才知道，那石板上刻的是一个方士的预言——说他会当皇帝。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "扫地-发现-被藏起-多年后才知道，宿命感", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_008", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "岳飞在军营里训练士兵，要求极其严格。一个新兵扎马步扎到双腿发抖。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "新兵哭着说：'将军，我实在撑不住了。'岳飞没有说话，在他旁边也扎起了马步。一个时辰后岳飞纹丝不动，新兵咬着牙跟着坚持到了最后。将军以身作则。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "严格训练-士兵受不了-以身作则-坚持", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_009", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "秦朝统一六国后，始皇帝下令修建长城。无数民夫被征召去服劳役。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个叫范喜良的年轻人被征去修长城，他的新婚妻子孟姜女日夜哭泣。范喜良在工地上累死了，被埋在长城脚下。孟姜女千里寻夫，哭倒了长城。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "修建长城-徭役-悲剧-千里寻夫，民间传说", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_010", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "永乐年间，郑和的宝船队即将第七次下西洋。船队在福建港口整装待发。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "船员们在做最后的补给，把瓷器、丝绸、茶叶装船。郑和站在旗舰船头，望着远方的海平线。他知道这一去又要好几年，但天子的使命必须完成。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "郑和下西洋-准备-启航，航海壮举", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_011", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "成吉思汗年少时，父亲被仇人毒死，部落四分五裂。他带着母亲和弟弟在草原上艰难求生。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "铁木真在河里抓鱼时被几个仇家的孩子围住。他没有害怕，反而冷静地说：'你们今天是来打架的，还是来结盟的？'那些孩子被他的气势镇住了。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "少年磨难-被围困-冷静应对-领袖气质", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_012", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "唐太宗李世民在玄武门之变前夜，辗转难眠。他知道明天将改变一切。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "长孙皇后端来一碗安神汤，轻声说：'如果明天出了事，我替你担着。'李世民握住她的手说：'我若成，你便是皇后；我若败，你便是我唯一的牵挂。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "历史转折-夫妻情深-决断，情感细腻", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_013", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "包拯在天长县当县令时，接手了一桩离奇的命案——死者身上没有伤口。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "包拯仔细检查尸体，发现死者的鼻孔中有少量白色粉末。他让仵作用银针试毒，银针变黑。经过追查，找到了用砒霜杀人的凶手。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "命案-检查-发现毒物-破案，包拯断案", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_014", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "赤壁之战前，周瑜和诸葛亮在商议火攻之策。但万事俱备，只欠东风。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "诸葛亮说他有办法借来东风。周瑜半信半疑。诸葛亮在高台上设坛作法，三日后果然刮起了东南风。周瑜惊叹：'孔明真神人也！'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "火攻-借东风-成功，经典桥段", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_015", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "康熙皇帝微服私访，在一个小镇上的茶馆喝茶。他听到旁边的人在议论朝政。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个人说：'当今圣上什么都好，就是太信那些洋人的玩意儿。'康熙不动声色地问：'此话怎讲？'那人滔滔不绝地说了一堆。康熙听完笑着说：'洋为中用，有何不可？'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "微服私访-听到议论-不动声色-巧妙回应", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_016", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "丝绸之路上的一个驿站，来自不同国家的商人们在此歇脚。骆驼铃声此起彼伏。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个波斯商人向一个唐朝商人展示他的地毯，唐朝商人则拿出了精美的瓷器。两人虽然语言不通，但比划着完成了交易。驿站老板给每人倒了一碗热茶。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "丝路驿站-跨国交易-比划+热茶，生动", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_017", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "科举考试放榜的日子，一个书生从早上就在榜前等着。他从天亮等到天黑。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "天黑了，榜上还是没有他的名字。书生失魂落魄地往回走。一个乞丐追上来：'公子，你的东西掉了。'书生一看——是他的准考证，他根本没进场。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "等榜-没中-发现根本没考试-喜剧反转", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_018", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "王安石推行变法，遭到了司马光等保守派的强烈反对。两人在朝堂上激烈争辩。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "王安石说：'不变法，国家就富不起来。'司马光说：'乱变法，百姓就要受苦。'两人各执一词。退朝后，两人在宫门外相遇，互相拱了拱手，各自离去。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "变法之争-朝堂辩论-政敌相敬，历史厚重感", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_019", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "三国时期，关羽在曹营中收到了刘备的来信。他看完信后热泪盈眶。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "曹操知道后，特意派人为关羽准备了行装。关羽骑着赤兔马，带着二位嫂嫂过五关斩六将，千里走单骑去寻找刘备。曹操感叹说：'云长真义士也！'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "收到故主来信-辞别-千里寻兄，义薄云天", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_020", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "大唐诗人王勃在滕王阁上，看到壮丽的江景，诗兴大发。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "他提笔写道：'落霞与孤鹜齐飞，秋水共长天一色。'满座宾客拍案叫绝。王勃放下笔，又连写了几首，每一首都是传世之作。这一天成为中国文学史上的高峰。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "登阁-灵感-写就千古名篇，文学盛事", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_021", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "明末，李自成兵临北京城下。崇祯皇帝在煤山上望着城外的火光。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个太监跑来报告：'皇上，城门被攻破了！'崇祯叹了口气，写下最后一道圣旨：'朕非亡国之君，而诸臣皆亡国之臣也。'然后自缢于煤山。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "城破-绝命-遗诏-殉国，悲壮历史", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_022", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "霍去病十七岁时第一次随卫青出征匈奴。他带着八百骑兵深入大漠。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "旁人劝他：'将军，不可冒进！'霍去病说：'兵贵神速，打了就跑。'他率军直捣匈奴大营，斩敌两千余人，俘虏了匈奴单于的叔父。少年将军一战成名。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "少年将军-深入敌后-大胜-一战成名", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_023", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "范仲淹在岳阳楼上眺望洞庭湖，感慨万千。他想起自己被贬的经历。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "他提笔写道：'先天下之忧而忧，后天下之乐而乐。'这句千古名言道出了一个士大夫的胸襟。写完后他把笔一扔，仰头大笑。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "登楼-感叹-写名句-士大夫情怀", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_024", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "张骞出使西域，在路上被匈奴扣留了十年。他每天都在想着完成使命。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "十年后他终于找到机会逃了出来，继续西行。他到达大宛国时，已经衣衫褴褛，但他依然挺直了腰杆，拿出了汉朝的符节。大宛王被他的精神感动了。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "被扣十年-不忘使命-继续西行-精神感人", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_025", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "大唐安史之乱爆发，长安城陷入混乱。百姓们拖家带口地逃难。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个书生在逃难路上看到有人在抢劫老妇人的包裹。他冲上去大喝一声：'住手！'虽然自己也是个文弱书生，但他不能看到这种事发生在眼前。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "战乱-逃难-见义勇为-书生挺身而出", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_026", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "武则天还是才人时，太宗皇帝有一匹烈马叫狮子骢，没人能驯服。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "武则天说：'我能驯服它，但需要三样东西——铁鞭、铁锤和匕首。先用鞭子抽，不服就用锤子打，再不服就用匕首杀了它。'太宗听后沉默良久。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "驯马-霸气回应-太宗沉默，武则天个性", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_027", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "南宋年间，岳飞被十二道金牌召回临安。他站在长江边上，久久不愿离开。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "将士们跪了一地：'将军，金兵就要渡江了，我们真的要走吗？'岳飞没有回头，声音沙哑地说：'君命不可违。'他跨上马，再也没有回头看过这片他浴血奋战的土地。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "金牌召回-将士挽留-军令如山-悲壮离别", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_028", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "曹操在官渡之战中以少胜多，击败了袁绍。战后清点袁绍的书信。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "士兵发现了很多曹操手下与袁绍暗通的书信。士兵要把写信的人抓起来，曹操却下令把书信全部烧毁。他说：'当时我自己都差点撑不住，何况别人？'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "大胜-发现通敌信件-烧信-宽宏大度", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_029", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "一个书生进京赶考，路上遇到一个同路的考生。两人边走边聊。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "聊到各自的理想时，一个说想当宰相，一个说想当太医。两人约好：'将来你当宰相治国，我当太医救人。'他们击掌为誓。多年后两人都实现了梦想。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "赶考路上-谈理想-相约-实现，励志故事", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_030", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "汉朝昭君出塞和亲，离开长安的那天，她在城门口回头看了一眼故土。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "她知道这一去再也回不来了。匈奴的迎亲队伍在城外等候，她弹起琵琶，曲声中满是思乡之情。南飞的大雁听到琴声，纷纷坠落——'沉鱼落雁'中的'落雁'。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "和亲-离别-弹琵琶-大雁落，凄美典故", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_031", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "清朝年间，纪晓岚在编纂四库全书时，发现了一本奇书。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "书上记载了很多前朝的秘闻，很多内容与他所知的历史不符。他决定如实收录，旁边的编修提醒他：'这些内容可能会惹麻烦。'纪晓岚笑了笑：'修史就要实事求是。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "编书-发现秘闻-如实收录-实事求是", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_032", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "三国时期，赵云在长坂坡单枪匹马杀入曹军重围。他怀中抱着阿斗。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "曹军大将们看到赵云一人冲阵，纷纷围了上来。赵云左手持枪右手舞剑，杀了个七进七出。曹操在高台上看到这一幕，连连赞叹：'真虎将也！下令活捉他。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "单骑救主-七进七出-曹操赞叹，经典场景", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_033", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "李白在长安城名气很大，被唐玄宗召见。玄宗让他写诗助兴。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "李白让高力士为他脱靴，杨国舅为他研墨。玄宗笑着说：'也只有你敢这样。'李白提笔写下：'云想衣裳花想容，春风拂槛露华浓。'玄宗大悦。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "李白入宫-让力士脱靴-写清平调-才气纵横", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_034", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "一个蒙古少年在草原上放羊，突然遇到了狼群。他只有一把弓和十几支箭。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "少年没有慌张，他先射死了头狼，然后对着天空大喊。附近的牧民听到声音赶来，一起赶走了狼群。少年的父亲摸着儿子的头说：'你长大了。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "遇狼-冷静射杀头狼-呼救-成长", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_035", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "大唐安西都护府的将士们已经驻守西域几十年了。很多人头发都白了。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个年轻的士兵问老将军：'将军，我们什么时候能回家？'老将军望着远处的雪山说：'等西域彻底太平了。'他摸了摸腰间的剑，这把剑已经陪了他四十年。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "戍边-思乡-坚守-老将军的回答，苍凉", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_036", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "王安石变法失败后，被罢相回到江宁。他在半山园中种花养草。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "司马光上台后废除了所有新法。有人来告诉王安石新法被废的消息，王安石正在给花浇水。他手没有停，只是淡淡地说：'知道了。'水壶中的水依然均匀地洒在花瓣上。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "被罢相-种花-听到消息-淡然面对，宠辱不惊", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_037", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "隋炀帝下令开凿大运河，数百万民夫在工地上劳作。一个年轻民夫在挖土时挖出了一块石碑。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "石碑上刻着奇怪的文字，没人看得懂。一个老儒生看了半天说：'这是预言——此河通，隋朝亡。'年轻民夫吓得赶紧把石碑扔回了河里。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "开运河-发现预言碑-害怕-扔回河中", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_038", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "蔺相如完璧归赵后，赵王封他为上大夫。老将廉颇不服气。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "廉颇说：'我在战场上出生入死，他凭一张嘴就爬到我头上？'蔺相如听说后，每次出门都主动避让廉颇。门客不解，蔺相如说：'将相和则国强，将相不和则国弱。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "完璧归赵-廉颇不服-蔺相如避让-将相和", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_039", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "光绪皇帝想要变法图强，但慈禧太后掌握着实权。他在紫禁城中感到窒息。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "康有为上书建议改革。光绪看后热血沸腾，但他知道每一步都会遭到太后的反对。他在奏折上批了'准'字，手却在发抖。旁边的太监垂着眼，假装什么都没看到。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "光绪-变法-太后干政-无奈与恐惧", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_040", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "明朝郑和宝船队到达了非洲东海岸，当地人从未见过这么大的船。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "船员们下船与当地人交易，用瓷器和丝绸换来了象牙和香料。一个当地首领问翻译：'你们是从天上来的吗？'翻译笑着说：'我们是从大明来的。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "郑和到非洲-交易-当地人的惊叹", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_041", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "hard", "input": {"preceding_context": "武则天登基前夕，一只白雀飞入了她的寝宫。侍从们都说是祥瑞。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "武则天看着白雀，想起了自己这一生的坎坷——从才人到尼姑，从尼姑到皇后，从皇后到皇帝。她伸手，白雀落在她指尖上。她轻声说：'天意？人意？'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "登基前-白雀-回忆一生-天意人意，有深度", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_042", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "魏征在朝堂上当面批评唐太宗，言辞激烈。太宗气得要杀他。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "退朝后长孙皇后换上朝服来贺喜。太宗不解，皇后说：'君明则臣直。魏征敢于直谏，说明陛下是明君。'太宗转怒为喜，从此更重视魏征的意见。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "直谏-太宗发怒-皇后劝解-明君直臣", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_043", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "一个来自波斯的商人在长安开了一家胡饼店。他做的胡饼很受欢迎。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "有一天一个客人吃完胡饼没钱付账，窘迫得满脸通红。波斯老板摆了摆手说：'没关系，下次再给。'客人感激地说：'长安真是个好地方。'老板用生硬的汉语说：'长安，好。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "胡商开店-客人没钱-免单-长安好", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_044", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "韩信年轻时被一群混混欺负，被迫从一个混混的胯下钻过去。围观的人都在笑。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "韩信没有反抗，默默地钻了过去。多年后他成了大将军，回来找到那个混混。混混吓得跪地求饶。韩信却笑着说：'起来吧。当年如果没有你的侮辱，我可能不会那么拼命。'"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "胯下之辱-功成名就-原谅仇人-大丈夫胸怀", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_045", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "西施在溪边浣纱，水中的鱼儿看到她的倒影，忘记了游动，沉到了水底。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "一个路过的商人看到了这一幕，惊为天人。他打听到西施的身份后，把她推荐给了越王勾践。勾践看到西施后，制定了一个美人计的计划。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "沉鱼-被发现-献给越王-美人计开始", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_046", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "大唐诗人杜甫在安史之乱中逃难，一路看到百姓的苦难。他写下了'感时花溅泪'。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "在逃难的人群中，他看到一对老夫妻在路边哭泣——他们的儿子被抓去当兵了。杜甫把身上最后的干粮分给了他们，然后在路边坐下写下了'三吏三别'。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "逃难-目睹苦难-分干粮-写诗记录，诗史杜甫", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_047", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "三国时期，诸葛亮在五丈原病重。他躺在病榻上，还在安排军务。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "姜维跪在床前说：'丞相，您该休息了。'诸葛亮咳了几声说：'我受先帝托孤之重，不敢有丝毫懈怠。'他在病中写下了出师表，字字泣血。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "病重-安排的遗命-出师表-鞠躬尽瘁", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_historical_048", "genre": "historical", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "康熙皇帝在承德避暑山庄打猎，遇到了一只受伤的梅花鹿。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "康熙命人给鹿包扎伤口。侍卫说：'皇上，这是祥瑞啊。'康熙说：'万物皆有灵，见死不救不是天子所为。'鹿被放生后，康熙射箭时它又出现了，引着他找到了一处温泉。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "打猎-救鹿-放生-鹿报恩引路", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
